name: ULevelSequenceEditorSubsystem
doc:
ULevelSequenceEditorSubsystem
Subsystem for level sequence editor related utilities to scripts

methods.name: AddActors
methods.doc: Add existing actors to Sequencer. Tracks will be automatically added based on default track settings.

methods.name: AddActorsToBinding
methods.doc: Assigns the given actors to the binding

methods.name: ConvertToPossessable
methods.doc: Convert to possessable

methods.name: ConvertToSpawnable
methods.doc: Convert to spawnable. If there are multiple objects assigned to the possessable, multiple spawnables will be created.

methods.name: CopyBindings
methods.doc:
Copy bindings
The copied bindings will be saved to the clipboard as well as assigned to the ExportedText string.
The ExportedTest string can be used in conjunction with PasteBindings if, for example, pasting copy/pasting multiple
bindings without relying on a single clipboard.

methods.name: CopyFolders
methods.doc:
Copy folders
The copied folders will be saved to the clipboard as well as assigned to the ExportedText string.
The ExportedTest string can be used in conjunction with PasteFolders if, for example, pasting copy/pasting multiple
folders without relying on a single clipboard.

methods.name: CopySections
methods.doc:
Copy sections
The copied sections will be saved to the clipboard as well as assigned to the ExportedText string.
The ExportedTest string can be used in conjunction with PasteSections if, for example, pasting copy/pasting multiple
sections without relying on a single clipboard.

methods.name: CopyTracks
methods.doc:
Copy tracks
The copied tracks will be saved to the clipboard as well as assigned to the ExportedText string.
The ExportedTest string can be used in conjunction with PasteTracks if, for example, pasting copy/pasting multiple
tracks without relying on a single clipboard.

methods.name: CreateCamera
methods.doc: Create a cine camera actor and add it to Sequencer

methods.name: FixActorReferences
methods.doc: Attempts to automatically fix up broken actor references in the current scene

methods.name: GetCurveEditor
methods.doc: Retrieve the curve editor

methods.name: GetScriptingLayer
methods.doc: Retrieve the scripting layer

methods.name: PasteBindings
methods.doc:
Paste bindings
Paste bindings from the given TextToImport string (used in conjunction with CopyBindings).
If TextToImport is empty, the contents of the clipboard will be used.

methods.name: PasteFolders
methods.doc:
Paste folders
Paste folders from the given TextToImport string (used in conjunction with CopyFolders).
If TextToImport is empty, the contents of the clipboard will be used.

methods.name: PasteSections
methods.doc:
Paste sections
Paste sections from the given TextToImport string (used in conjunction with CopySections).
If TextToImport is empty, the contents of the clipboard will be used.

methods.name: PasteTracks
methods.doc:
Paste tracks
Paste tracks from the given TextToImport string (used in conjunction with CopyTracks).
If TextToImport is empty, the contents of the clipboard will be used.

methods.name: RebindComponent
methods.doc: Rebind the component binding to the requested component

methods.name: RemoveActorsFromBinding
methods.doc: Removes the given actors from the binding

methods.name: RemoveAllBindings
methods.doc: Remove all bound actors from this track

methods.name: RemoveInvalidBindings
methods.doc: Remove missing objects bound to this track

methods.name: ReplaceBindingWithActors
methods.doc: Replaces the binding with the given actors

methods.name: SnapSectionsToTimelineUsingSourceTimecode
methods.doc: Snap sections to timeline using source timecode

methods.name: SyncSectionsUsingSourceTimecode
methods.doc: Sync section using source timecode
